criteria.textblock:
Inclusion Criteria:

  -  diagnosis of OSA;

  -  18-75 years;

  -  CPAP recommendation;

  -  Informed consent.

Exclusion Criteria:

  -  Disabling hypersomnia;

  -  Pregnancy;

  -  Psychiatric disorders;

  -  Previous treatment with CPAP;

  -  Clinical instability in the previous month;

  -  Inability to use information technologies (computers and web).
